Add ghdl to your flake.nix devShell packages.

Edit flake.nix, find this block:

          yosys
          nextpnr
          openfpgaloader
          picocom
          usbutils
          pkgsCross.riscv32-embedded.buildPackages.gcc

And add `ghdl` (any position works):

          yosys
          nextpnr
          openfpgaloader
          picocom
          usbutils
          ghdl                                   # ← add this line
          pkgsCross.riscv32-embedded.buildPackages.gcc

Then exit the shell and re-enter:

  exit
  nix develop

Verify:

  which ghdl
  ghdl --version | head -1

If you want a unified-diff to apply with `patch -p1` instead:

--- a/flake.nix
+++ b/flake.nix
@@ -22,6 +22,7 @@
           yosys
           nextpnr
           openfpgaloader
           picocom
           usbutils
+          ghdl
           pkgsCross.riscv32-embedded.buildPackages.gcc
